    subLevel: SubLevel.EXPERT,
    question: `A casino manager notices that players who believe in the Gambler's Fallacy tend to stay at tables longer after losing streaks. How does this behavioral pattern translate into increased casino revenue?`,
    options: ["Gambler's Fallacy", "Hot Hand Fallacy", "Survivorship Bias", "False Cause"],
